>\n<li>明天（ 28 号）中午 12 点之前的楼层</li>\n<li>使用 @bfhyqy 在 t/1106143 提供的抽奖工具</li>\n<li>另外只要回复本帖我就会感谢铜币（直到送完）</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>额外服务</h2>\n<p>大家如果有 stripe/stripe atlas 之类的问题也可以问我，如果想在 stripe atlas 注册公司，那么我可以提供五折注册的优惠码（无任何利益相关）。</p>\n<p>最后，谢谢。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1740621042, "replies": 64, "id": 1114522}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_large.png?m=1650127623", "name": "shenzhen", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_normal.png?m=1650127623", "title": "深圳", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/shenzhen", "topics": 3265, "footer": "", "header": "", "title_alternative": "Shenzhen", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/3c59/dc04/21_mini.png?m=1650127623", "stars": 2035, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 21, "parent_node_name": "cn"}, "member": {"id": 259998, "username": "kgloveyou", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/kgloveyou", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d902df4c5fe865856a98eb63b5df8cf0?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d902df4c5fe865856a98eb63b5df8cf0?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/d902df4c5fe865856a98eb63b5df8cf0?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1508135921, "last_modified": 1508135921}, "last_reply_by": "hailaz", "last_touched": 1740630960, "title": "深圳电动自行车载人要开罚单了？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1114494", "created": 1740617424, "deleted": 0, "content": "早上被交警拦住了，说载人超过 1.2m 了，给开了罚单。目前，没查到具体这条规定的依据。", "content_rendered": "<p>早上被交警拦住了，说载人超过 1.2m 了，给开了罚单。目前，没查到具体这条规定的依据。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1740617424, "replies": 61, "id": 1114494}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9f61/408e/56_large.png?m=1628212285", "name": "internet", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/9f61/408e/56_normal.png?m=1628212285", "title": "互联网", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/internet", "topics": 3869, "footer": "", "header": "In 